headline: Royal Caribbean Cruises (NYSE:RCL) Outperforms With 11% Gain Over Last Week
summary: Royal Caribbean Cruises (NYSE:RCL) experienced a notable price movement last week with a 11% rise, amidst a backdrop of mixed market performances. Despite broader concerns about economic conditions, including potential tariffs and a recession outlook, Royal Caribbean managed to outperform.
